Ticket ID: ITSEC-003-AWS-MFA
Date: 06-Nov-2025
Reported by: testuser@ayotech.com

Issue: Lost MFA device — unable to log in.
Impact: Access to AWS console and resources blocked.

Resolution Steps:

Verified user identity through HR confirmation.

Admin removed old MFA from IAM console.

Re-assigned MFA to user’s new Authenticator app.

Login verified with new MFA device.

Preventive Measures:

Encourage backup MFA methods (hardware key or SMS).

Implement account recovery workflow.

Store backup codes in secure location.
